st||md|1,,SkJ8 HKQ9 D754 C9843,|sv|0|rh||ah|Example 7|mb|1nd|lb|*bWhat would you bid with the hand shown above?^^r|mb|r|AN|Partner I have 8+ points|NT|^B@2
Of course again you can ignore the double and bid 2NT if you wish.|
PG| ***** 169 ***** |


NT|^B@2
So |cp|8|at|IGNORE the double|cp||at| after the NT opening and bid as you usually do. That is simple.|
