^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|After a 2S overcall responder should bid 3C or 3D showing 5+ card in that suit with 10+ points and no spade stopper. The 1N opener should bid 3N with a spade stopper, pass with no spade stopper.|
PG| ***** 196 ***** |


