^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|3H by responder is natural with 10+ points. Does not promise or deny a spade stopper. The opener should bid 4H with 3+ hearts - as shown above. With 2 hearts, opener bids 3N with a spade stopper and 3S without a spade stopper - we will see more.|
