^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|3H by responder is natural with 10+ points. Does not promise or deny a spade stopper. The opener should bid 4H with 3+ hearts, with 2 hearts, opener bids 3N with a spade stopper - as we saw in the previous boards.|
